{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 284418, "create_time": 1657362564, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "问题是，我所写的两种解法，差别在哪，究竟哪个是正确的。", "timestamp": 1657362564}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 284442, "create_time": 1657363381, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "u是啥", "timestamp": 1657363381}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 284444, "create_time": 1657363432, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 二者相对速度", "timestamp": 1657363432}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 284465, "create_time": 1657363898, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: ①对应O’系的相遇②对应O系的相遇吧", "timestamp": 1657363898}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 284476, "create_time": 1657364105, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "记不太清了，方法2的式子好像错了吧，因子应该在下面吧\n", "timestamp": 1657364105}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 284601, "create_time": 1657366877, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "答案解法是第二个方法，一和二对应的都是O'系相遇，就是固有时应该是O'系中的相遇时间。", "timestamp": 1657366877}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 284862, "create_time": 1657374310, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "dz对洛伦兹变换的理解很不正确啊😂先想一想，你设的两个事件真的是事件吗？", "timestamp": 1657374310}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 284877, "create_time": 1657374948, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: O在O所在参考系同时测量O和O'位置，这两个事件。这有什么问题吗？就大物学了下狭义相对论，认识可能确实有问题，也许我对一些东西的不理解就在这个问题上。", "timestamp": 1657374948}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 284884, "create_time": 1657375072, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 事件1，在O系测量O所在位置，事件2，在O系中与事件1同一时刻测量O'的位置。", "timestamp": 1657375072}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 284885, "create_time": 1657375153, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 我纸上写的确实没描述清楚，给你感觉我是定义的两个时空坐标是吧，但我就是按照事件去定义的。", "timestamp": 1657375153}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 285157, "create_time": 1657384352, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "记L=20m，取S'系相对于O以-0.6c运动，*O系中初始时测量O‘位置*事件坐标为$[x_1,ct_1]=[L,0]$，变换到S’系中坐标为$[x_1',ct_1']=[\\gamma L,\\gamma\\beta L]$;*O系中OO‘相遇*事件坐标为$[x_2,ct_2]=[0,L/\\beta]$，变换到S‘系中坐标为$[x_2',ct_2']=[\\gamma L,\\gamma L/\\beta]$，要求的时间就是$\\Delta t'=t_2'-t_1'=L/(c\\beta\\gamma)$也就是②里面的答案", "timestamp": 1657384352}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 285165, "create_time": 1657384579, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "dz把①里面的x2'-x1'当成O’系中的初始距离了吧，这是不对的，从结果来看相当于对OO‘做了次尺缩，但问题是OO'不构成”尺子“", "timestamp": 1657384579}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 285190, "create_time": 1657385050, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Dave: 牛啊，简洁明了", "timestamp": 1657385050}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 285198, "create_time": 1657385172, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Dave: 谢谢啦，也就是说从结果来看的尺缩，其实并不是真正的尺缩，只是碰巧如此是吧。也就是不能用尺缩来理解这个问题。", "timestamp": 1657385172}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 285218, "create_time": 1657385522, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Dave: 还想问一下，我1里面定义的两个事件是不能构成事件吗？也就是为什么不能把我定义的x2'-x1'当成初始距离。", "timestamp": 1657385522}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 285224, "create_time": 1657385837, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "我好像明白了，题目并没有说明O系测量距离是不是同时，而我默认为同时了。", "timestamp": 1657385837}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 285226, "create_time": 1657385956, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Eve: 你说的这个x2’-x1‘实际上就是我第一条回复里说的x1’，它只是*O初始时测量O‘位置*这个事件在S‘系里面的x**坐标**，不是**距离**，距离应该是两个坐标的差，你还得求出来S'系中对应时刻O的位置才能算”距离“", "timestamp": 1657385956}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 285241, "create_time": 1657387789, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Dave: 为什么不能这么定义，定义O系初始时刻测量O位置事件坐标为（x1,ct1）=（0，0）测量O'位置事件坐标为x2,ct2=（L,0），转换到O'中，然后用x2'-x1'除以相对速度", "timestamp": 1657387789}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 285243, "create_time": 1657387961, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Dave: 就我得到在O'系中的两个坐标，作差，得到初始相对距离，除以速度，得到时间。", "timestamp": 1657387961}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 285245, "create_time": 1657387993, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "*O系初始时刻测量O位置*这个事件和*测量O'位置*这个事件在O’中不是同时发生的呀，这么算出来的也不是距离...必须得在O'中同一时刻得到O的坐标与O‘的坐标才行", "timestamp": 1657387993}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 285249, "create_time": 1657388725, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Dave: 哦哦哦，我明白了，非常感谢，解决了我的困惑。", "timestamp": 1657388725}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 285252, "create_time": 1657389371, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Dave: 这样就没问题了，在我的定义中，定义第三个事件，在O'系中t2'时刻测量O的位置，那么x3'＝(t2'-t1')×u，再把x3'-x2'的结果，除以u，就对啦", "timestamp": 1657389371}], "create_time": 1657362503, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1657389371, "likenum": 10, "n_attentions": 10, "n_comments": 22, "pid": 80465, "poll": null, "reply": 22, "text": "两个惯性系中的观察者O和O’以0.6c（c表示真空中光速)的相对速度互相接近。如果O测得两者的初始距离是20m,则O’测得两者经过时间△t'=___________.s后相遇。\n![](https://bafybeiazyw3mpuovd4at5ediqkdz6424xsfzzol43jhdyepasqudjvmvui.ipfs.infura-ipfs.io/?filename=IMG_20220709_182803.jpg&filetype=image%2Fjpeg) [加载失败请点击此](https://t-hole.red/ipfs.html#bafybeiazyw3mpuovd4at5ediqkdz6424xsfzzol43jhdyepasqudjvmvui)\n\n---\n", "timestamp": 1657362503}}